{
  "stem": "5639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But one habit remained was he was the heavy smoking, and what I think now is that he contracted lung cancer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the doctor advised him to go to Berlin and undergo an operation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the year was before my birth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It must have been '21, 1921.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went to a rabbi, as it was the wont of Jews at that time, and the rabbi told him to go and to have the operation, and he died soon after the operation.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He never came back to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Berlin.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, they brought his body back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his sons, in bitterness and resentment, went to see the rabbi, and they said, how could you advise my father-- how could you advise my father, go to Berlin and have the operation?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Look what happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, he was a too good man to stuffer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He knew, and he said, he was a too good man to suffer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they brought the body back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The family was devastated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was the first-born grandchild after his death.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as his name was Hanoch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was named-- Hanoch, which means, more or less, in Polish Henry-- and I was named Henrika.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the story of my name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, there is another beautiful story that my mother actually intended to call me, if I am a girl, Michelle, and if a boy, Michal.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as she was in labor with me, and going to hospital was only for poor people, so she was in labor in our own place, surrounded by family, mothers, and sisters.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in between the labor pain, she fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She dozed off, and she dreamt that her father came to see her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was his favorite--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Daughter.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--everybody says she was his favorite daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
